<ServiceHero
  eyebrow="Lights Then Dies · Thermocouple · Gas Pressure · Wind Sensor · LA Same-Day"
  title="Patio Heater Flame Out Repair Los Angeles"
  subtitle={`Lights initially then flames out, runs briefly then dies, won't stay lit through normal operation. Same-day diagnostic across LA, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, Riverside. $120 outdoor diagnostic, waived with repair. ${phone}`}
  heroImageTitle="Patio Heater Flame Out Repair"
