    <h2 class="section-title">Flame-out repair costs.</h2>
    <p class="lead">$120 outdoor diagnostic, waived with repair. Universal pricing across residential and commercial. Duty cycle (residential 50-200 hr/yr vs commercial 8-14 hr daily) accelerates parts wear timeline; pricing structure stays $120 universal.</p>
